.container
    .row.login
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.snapScreen
            .panel.panel-default
                .panel-body
                    .alert.alert-success.text-center(role="alert" ng-show="confirmed && ready")
                        | Your account is active. Proceed to
                        a( href="#/login" ng-show="role==='any'")
                            |  Login
                        a( href="#/feed" ng-show="role==='user'")
                            |  Home
                        a( href="#/" ng-show="role==='admin'")
                            |  Admin Dashboard
                    .alert.alert-danger.text-center(role="alert" ng-show="!confirmed && ready")
                        | Error, please try again.